From: Sam <samuelngs@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sun, 10 May 2026 20:46:20 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 12/15] window: set default viewport to 1920x942 (maximized on
 3840x2160 @2x)

Matches a maximized Chrome window on a 3840x2160 display at 2x DPR:
1920x1080 logical screen, 50px work area top, 88px browser chrome.
Viewport = 1920 x (1080 - 50 - 88) = 1920 x 942.

diff --git a/headless/public/headless_browser.h b/headless/public/headless_browser.h
index 2669a6bb8c..487b734cae 100644
--- a/headless/public/headless_browser.h
+++ b/headless/public/headless_browser.h
@@ -109,7 +109,7 @@ struct HEADLESS_EXPORT HeadlessBrowser::Options {
 
   // Default window size. This is also used to create the window tree host and
   // as the headless screen size. Defaults to 800x600.
-  gfx::Size window_size = gfx::Size(800, 600);
+  gfx::Size window_size = gfx::Size(1920, 942);
 
   // Headless screen info specification.
   std::string screen_info_spec;
